{"tid":2192580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"制服繃炸！世新校花趁下課10分鐘　解扣「彈出雪乳」透氣","createTime":"2020-09-07T08:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T01:42:50.000Z","uid":217211,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"01f77d41fc0b5e28630091480d536da3ad753674","tid":2192580,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"「世新校花」陳葳在15歲曾參加過《我猜我猜我猜猜》爆紅，擁有魔鬼身材的她，從不吝嗇展現自己火辣的胴體，分別在臉書、IG都有著破20萬人的追蹤數，人氣相當高，她曬出穿上制服的照片，趁著「下課十分鐘」的時候，把繃緊緊的鈕扣一一解開，解放胸前豐滿白皙雪乳，勾起許多男網友的遐想。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/29/2744964-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2F2744964-PH.jpg&h=ee903056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/13/2661408-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F13%2F2661408-XXL.jpg&h=0b8fce96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳葳PO出以「校園」當作主題的照片，其中一張場景是在教室內，她用蝴蝶結綁了公主頭，穿著粉白相間條紋上衣，扣子解到胸前位置，小露迷人雙峰和極致深線，雙手部分則扶著課桌邊緣，往前撲露出充滿好奇心的神情，給人一種可愛活潑的美感，不少網友看到後，暴動留言「喜歡美麗、性感，充滿魅力的妳，妳是我的最愛」、「太太太可愛了」、「仙女」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/29/2744965-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2F2744965-PH.jpg&h=2f1eef96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/29/2744963-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2F2744963-PH.jpg&h=c7ab25d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更誘人的是，陳葳曬出另外一組照片、影片，這次她換上純白襯衫，下半身搭配格紋百褶裙，一雙長白襪，完全滿足男人們的幻想。她在影片部分，把襯衫扣子往下解了二顆，原本被包緊緊雪乳終於能出來喘口氣，加上她走向鏡頭前，超多網友都把目光放在美胸上「目不轉睛」，而陳葳在配文寫下「下課十分鐘」，後面附上吐舌頭的表情符號，非常俏皮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/29/2744961-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2F2744961-PH.jpg&h=9fc79c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/29/2744962-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F29%2F2744962-PH.jpg&h=0625fa15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bedc9290fbf471f4fc861fa7e61bf23cb862794","tid":2192580,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a7774a95785aa822d7e4a3fd2164465684ecb3","tid":2192580,"uid":38172,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"又係呢D樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ebf4e7e98724a6907127e77b7de66111d0cc27","tid":2192580,"uid":75337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"85a7774a95785aa822d7e4a3fd2164465684ecb3","tid":2192580,"uid":38172,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"又係呢D樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"對眼好攰"},{"pid":"0e5c556a21698eb89ed8e6f0047f86f259ce443b","tid":2192580,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"賢者之石產物"},{"pid":"ba15eb4374d0e9e9fe8ba80dc5bdb52342fcadeb","tid":2192580,"uid":249094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c9ebf4e7e98724a6907127e77b7de66111d0cc27","tid":2192580,"uid":75337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"85a7774a95785aa822d7e4a3fd2164465684ecb3","tid":2192580,"uid":38172,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"又係呢D樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"對眼好攰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020